{"tid":1406453,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每人拎一支呀媽卸甲水防身","createTime":"2019-08-04T13:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T13:46:13.000Z","uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8ee943817e39b8e804ef518c0e0d5d8ea45af05d","tid":1406453,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:23:53.000Z","msg":"狗想玩colour party，各位拎多啲衫同鞋換。<br />\n個袋要有垃圾袋包好<br />\n身上顏料要用卸甲水同毛巾抹。<br />\n有剩卸甲水淋到狗盾同狗頭盔。<br />\n<br />\n因為卸甲油有acetone成份。<br />\n<br />\n遇上polycarbonate ，就脆過脆皮腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無chem人士可以查証下？"},{"pid":"59f7af39a55d032aec572fd164fbb567f9f78242","tid":1406453,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:25:02.000Z","msg":"買黃豆 + 油 有無用 ？想線死班狗隻"},{"pid":"81e3736f0fa7d8effa3c90489fb495752d7ce85b","tid":1406453,"uid":54014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:31:08.000Z","msg":"無記錯都係acetone,alcohol同ethyl acetate。<br />\n而一般實驗室都係以acetone洗野包括dye。<br />\n一提係可以試下消毒火酒洗，isopropyl alcohol都算溶得下。<br />\n有興趣知成份可以睇哩篇:<br />\n<a href=\"https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ed074p1464\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubs.acs.org%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1021%2Fed074p1464&d=8tXbBdGphLRwD8DFuLHjuLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=c0bfeb0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ed074p1464</a>"},{"pid":"64289097bdc36cf57ebe3cb425419bdde84eb419","tid":1406453,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:38:16.000Z","msg":"但火酒好危險，但易燃，啲狗一射彈就gg"},{"pid":"662cf9f7348b57efa08d2899ec562f4209a52e98","tid":1406453,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:43:55.000Z","msg":"Pushx10"},{"pid":"32e0031cd4928fd8626896d0b9343e4021a1016e","tid":1406453,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:44:06.000Z"